<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>About Us</title>
  <link href="public/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <script src="public/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" defer></script>
  <link href="/css/styles.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Load Navbar From /assets/partials/navbar -->
  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

  <!-- Page Content -->
  <main class="container mt-5 pt-5" id="about-us">
    <div class="card shadow-sm rounded-4 p-4">
      <div class="card-body text-center">

        <!-- About Our Program -->
        <section id="program" class="mb-5">
          <h1 class="section-title my-4" id="about-program">About our Program</h1>

          <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-8">
              <h2 class="pb-3">STR5EAM Erasmus+ @ PPMG - Vratsa</h2>

              <p class="mb-3 pb-2">
                The Secondary School of Science and Mathematics "Akademician Ivan Tsenov" - Vratsa is a holder of long-term 
                accreditation under the Erasmus+ program (KA120-SCH). The main goal of our project is to 
                transform the learning environment through an innovative and interdisciplinary approach to STEM education, 
                complemented by arts and responsible research.
              </p>

              <h2 class="mb-3">What is STR5EAM?</h2>
              <p class="mb-3 fw-semibold">
                STR5EAM is an upgrade of the traditional STEM model that includes five key R-components and the arts (Art), 
                placing students at the center of learning through creation, discovery, and teamwork.
              </p>

              <ul class="text-start mx-4">
                <li><strong>Recreation</strong> - learning through games, escape rooms, puzzles and fun science activities</li>
                <li><strong>Reading</strong> - developing functional literacy and understanding of scientific texts</li>
                <li><strong>Robotics</strong> - learning digital and algorithmic skills through robotics</li>
                <li><strong>Relation</strong> - solving real social and environmental problems through STEM projects</li>
                <li><strong>Research</strong> - building skills for responsible research and innovation</li>
                <li><strong>Art</strong> - using visual and performing arts to express scientific ideas</li>
              </ul>

              <h3 class="my-4">Our vision</h3>
              <p class="mb-3">
                STR5EAM is an educational model that prepares students not just to acquire knowledge, but to create, 
                communicate, and implement solutions in the real world. The project stimulates creativity, teamwork, and social responsibility.
              </p>

              <p class="mb-3">
                Thanks to Erasmus+ accreditation, students and teachers participate in international training, 
                exchanges and activities that build new horizons and develop key skills of the future.
              </p>

              <img src="../assets/img/stem/ppmg_erasmus_boot.png" class="img-fluid rounded mb-4" alt="Erasmus+ Program" />
              <p class="mb-3 fw-semibold">
                The core of the Erasmus+ project lies in building strong international relationships 
                between educational facilities. Through various exchange programs, schools and 
                universities work together on joint projects, share teaching methods, and explore innovative approaches to learning.
              </p>

              <img src="../assets/img/stem/ppmg_sci3.png" class="img-fluid rounded mb-4" alt="Erasmus+ Program" />
              <p class="mb-3 fw-semibold">
                These partnerships encourage the exchange of knowledge, culture, and experiences, 
                allowing participants to develop a deeper understanding of different educational systems 
                and perspectives.
              </p>

              <img src="../assets/img/stem/ppmg_sci2.png" class="img-fluid rounded mb-4" alt="Erasmus+ Program" />
              <p class="mb-3 fw-semibold">
                In addition to fostering collaboration, Erasmus+ promotes the development of key competencies 
                and skills that are essential for success in today's interconnected world.
              </p>

              <img src="../assets/img/stem/ppmg_dance.png" class="img-fluid rounded mb-4" alt="Erasmus+ Program" />
              <p class="mb-3 fw-semibold">
                Erasmus+ promotes unity through education, helping to create a network of schools that are open, cooperative, and committed to improving learning across borders.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <hr class="my-4" />

        <!-- About Our School -->
        <section id="school">
          <h1 class="section-title my-4" id="about-school">About our School</h1>

          <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-8">
              <p class="mb-3 fw-semibold">
                The Secondary School of Science and Mathematics "Akademician Ivan Tsenov" in Vratsa 
                is one of the leading educational institutions in Bulgaria, renowned 
                for its strong emphasis on science, technology, engineering, and mathematics (STEM).
              </p>

              <img src="../assets/img/stem/viber_image_2025-04-14_13-33-32-998.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded mb-4" alt="School image" />
              <p class="mb-3 fw-semibold">
                Named after the esteemed Bulgarian academician Ivan Tsenov, the school embodies a commitment 
                to providing students with a solid foundation in mathematics and the natural sciences, alongside a well-rounded education in the humanities and social sciences.
              </p>

              <img src="../assets/img/stem/ppmg_ceremony.png" class="img-fluid rounded mb-4" alt="Ceremony" />
              <p class="mb-3 fw-semibold">
                The school promotes a culture of academic achievement and innovation by actively 
                participating in national and international competitions in mathematics, physics, computer science, 
                and other disciplines.
              </p>

              <img src="../assets/img/stem/ppmg_bg_flag.png" class="img-fluid rounded mb-4" alt="Flag" />
              <p class="mb-3 fw-semibold">
                Beyond academics, the school encourages holistic development through extracurricular activities such as 
                sports, arts, cultural programs and European programs like Erasmus+, EPAS, OSOS and ENEN.
              </p>

              <img src="../assets/img/stem/ppmg_eu_flag.png" class="img-fluid rounded mb-4" alt="EU Flag" />
              <p class="mb-3 fw-semibold">
                With its dedicated faculty and commitment to excellence, the Secondary School of Science and Mathematics "Akademician Ivan Tsenov" 
                continues to be a source of pride for Vratsa and a beacon of educational distinction in Bulgaria.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

      </div> <!-- .card-body -->
    </div> <!-- .card -->
  </main>

  <!-- Footer-->
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>

  <!-- Custom Scripts Here-->
  <script src="js/scripts.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/translator.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
